            "title": "內地A股開市即跌逾1% 滬指開跌35點 深成指挫153點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中美關稅戰愈演愈烈，內地股市今早開市時應聲下滑，滬深股指齊挫逾1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-13.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-13.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指以3110點開市，跌35點或1.13%。深證成指開市報9271點，亦跌153點或1.63%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌44點或1.22%，開報3606點；創業板指數開市報1805點，跌34點或1.89%。</p>\n</div>",
