            "title": "港股開市︱再失二萬 關稅戰升級 恒指急挫632點開報19494",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">投資者對美國延遲實施關稅措施的願望落空，白宮更將貿易戰升級，對華部分貨品徵104%關稅，再度打擊環球金融市場。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20241230_FI_source-ap_US_China_Hack.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20241230_FI_source-ap_US_China_Hack.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股今早甫開市即再失守二萬點關口，以19494點開市，大跌632點或3.14%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報4373點，跌194點或4.26%；國企指數以7198點開市，跌232點或3.13%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230810_FI_source-web_09988-3-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230810_FI_source-web_09988-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股掉頭再挫，阿里巴巴(09988)跌穿百元大關，開報97.4元，跌4.98%；騰訊(00700)開報426元，跌3.27%；美團(03690)開報135元，跌3.98%。滙控(00005)開報70.45元，跌3.1%；友邦(01299)開報50.85元，跌4.33%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14840477-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%86%8d%e5%a4%b1%e4%ba%8c%e8%90%ac-%e9%97%9c%e7%a8%85%e6%88%b0%e5%8d%87%e7%b4%9a-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e6%80%a5%e6%8c%ab632%e9%bb%9e%e9%96%8b%e5%a0%b119494",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/HKS_source-bp_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-09 09:31:05",
