        {
            "title": "關稅戰拖累 即月期指開報19073點 低水1055點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">關稅戰愈演愈烈，環球股市今早重現動盪，港股亦難倖免，情況率先在期指市場反映。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報19073點，跌845點，較上日現貨收市價20127點低水1055點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報4250點，跌257點，低水318點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報6992點，跌349點，低水439點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14840457-%e9%97%9c%e7%a8%85%e6%88%b0%e6%8b%96%e7%b4%af-%e5%8d%b3%e6%9c%88%e6%9c%9f%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%a0%b119073%e9%bb%9e-%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b41055%e9%bb%9e",
